      <lg xml:id="TolE0239">
<l>patakkumuṉ variṉē tūṇik kiḷavi</l>
<l>mutaṟkiḷan teṭutta vēṟṟumai yiyaṟṟē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The nature of the demonstrative [<foreign xml:lang="ta">i</foreign>]</l>
<l>is the same as that mentioned before.<note
              place="foot">In other words : the demonstrative <foreign xml:lang="ta">i</foreign> behaves like the demonstrative <foreign xml:lang="ta">a :</foreign> e.g. <foreign xml:lang="ta">i +
          nūl &gt; innūl, i + yāḻ &gt; ivyāl</foreign> etc., cf. aphorisms 206-9.</note></l>
      </lg>
    </div>
